short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GetSales.io - Collect Leads, Find Emails & Phones, Export to CRM

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: GetSales.io is an Ai-Powered Sales Engagement Platform with Account-Based Approach and 1-to-1 Personalization. This Chrome Extension helps you to collect Contacts and Companies from LinkedIn in one click, find Emails and Phones and export to your CRM.
